The main analysis will be a 2 (condition: mortality salience vs. control priming task) × 2 
(ethnicity: European American vs. Asian American) multivariate ANOVA on the 
dependent variable of the Prostitution Attitudes Scale scores. The original paper found a 
significant interactive effect on PAS (Prostitution Attitudes Scale) score, F(1, 38) = 
10.263, p = .003 
 
 
 

 
 
